The 2018 MyBroadband Digital Marketing Conference took place at The Venue in Melrose Arch on 18 April, and attracted a full house of marketing professionals. The conference covered various aspects of digital marketing, including online publishing, content marketing, social media, creativity, email marketing, and native advertising. Speakers included Clockwork Media MD Tom Manners, brand communication specialist Musa Kalenga, Shift ONE CEO Dylan Kohlstädt, Between 10and5 MD Uno De Waal, and Everlytic marketing manager Karyn Strybos. Here is a look at what the delegates enjoyed at this year’s MyBroadband Digital Marketing Conference.                   